    "## 3. Load the Dataset\n",
    "\n",
    "The dataset is stored as newline-delimited JSON (`.jsonl`). Each line is one question with the following fields:\n",
    "\n",
    "| Field | Description |\n",
    "|---|---|\n",
    "| `id` | Unique question identifier |\n",
    "| `question` | Problem statement |\n",
    "| `options` | List of answer choices — present for **MCQ**, absent for **free-form** |\n",
    "| `answer` | Ground-truth answer (letter for MCQ, value/list for free-form) |"
   ]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "code",
   "execution_count": 5,
   "id": "23ee5092",
   "metadata": {
    "scrolled": true
   },
